'''烏理瑪'''（{{lang-ar| علماء}}，''{{transl|ar|DIN|ʿUlamāʾ }}''，單數形式： {{rtl-lang|ar|عالِم}} ，''{{transl|ar|DIN|ʿĀlim}}''；{{lang-en|Ulama}}或{{lang|en|ulema}}），又譯為'''烏里瑪'''、'''歐萊瑪'''，[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]原義為學者，是[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]學者的總稱。任何一位了解古蘭經注學、聖訓學、教義學、教法學，與有系統的宗教知識的學者，都可被稱為烏理瑪。它被用來泛指伊斯蘭教中所有的知識份子，包括[[阿訇|阿訇]]、[[毛拉|毛拉]]、[[伊瑪目|伊瑪目]]等。<ref name="jacb">{{cite book|last1 = Brown|first1 = Jonathan A.C. |author-link = Jonathan A.C. Brown|title = Misquoting Muhammad: The Challenge and Choices of Interpreting the Prophet's Legacy|date = 2014|publisher = [[Oneworld_Publications|Oneworld Publications]]|isbn = 978-1-78074-420-9|page = [https://archive.org/details/misquotingmuhamm0000brow/page/3 3]|quote = The ulama (literally, the learned ones)|url = https://archive.org/details/misquotingmuhamm0000brow/page/3}}</ref><ref name="Def_EI2">{{cite book| author1=Cl. Gilliot| author2=R.C. Repp| author3=K.A. Nizami| author4=M.B. Hooker| author5=Chang-Kuan Lin| author6=J.O. Hunwick| editor1-last=P. Bearman| editor1-first=P.| editor2-last=Bianquis| editor2-first=Th.| editor3-last=Bosworth| editor3-first=C.E.| editor4-last=van Donzel| editor4-first=E.| editor5-last=Heinrichs| editor5-first=W.P.| title=ʿUlamāʾ. In: Encyclopaedia of Islam| date=2012| publisher=E.J. Brill| location=Leiden| isbn=978-90-04-16121-4| edition=2| doi=10.1163/1573-3912_islam_COM_1278}}</ref>

